libaprs (1.0.2-1) stable; urgency=low

  * RTL-SDR receiver (aprs_sdr) with async IQ reader
  * 500ms silence lead-in and 50-flag preamble
  * Post-decimation audio scaling (fixes DC blocker saturation)
  * tx_level config for FM deviation control
  * 190 tests, zero allocation

